<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/514971-samuel-sachs-is-mentioned-in-the-book-as-a">Samuel Sachs is mentioned in the book as a salesman who joined the mortgage department of Salomon in 1979. However, the real Samuel died in 1935. Are the characters fictitious?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_514971'><a id="like_count_community_question_514971" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/514971?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F530198.Liar_s_Poker">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/514971-samuel-sachs-is-mentioned-in-the-book-as-a">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/514971-samuel-sachs-is-mentioned-in-the-book-as-a">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/51469454-dmitry-tregubov"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1580047543i/51469454._UY100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/51469454-dmitry-tregubov">Dmitry Tregubov</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
Obviously Samuel Sachs from Salomon Brothers has nothing in common with Samuel Sachs (1851 — 1935).
</span>
</div>
</div>
